credit_line: Gift of Mr. and Mrs. Abraham M. Adler
title: Psyche's father at the Oracle of Apollo
description: Set of scenic wallpaper "Les Amours de Psyche", consisting of 26 panels.  In grisaille.  Scene depicts Psyche resting her head on her mother's shoulder.  Her father stands to the left.  Cupid peers around the corner.
name: Scenic - panel
